WEBVTT

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:06.880
Shah Rukh Khan: How do we face
tomorrow's world in the right spirit?

00:00:06.880 --> 00:00:10.040
Who better than our next generation
to answer this?

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:13.800
In fact, if you think about it --
they are our tomorrow.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:17.800
Today on TED Talks India Nayi Soch
to teach us this,

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:20.600
we have with us from Chennai, 
Lydian Nadhswaram,

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:22.710
who has been learning music from the

00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:25.790
the globally acclaimed composer A.R. Rahman,

00:00:25.790 --> 00:00:29.080
and is now also composing
with the legend himself

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:32.000
just only at the age of 11 years.